Metallica - Worldwired Tour Phoenix,(Live 2-CD) 2017ak320


Metallica is an American heavy metal band formed in  California.
The band was formed in 1981 when vocalist/guitarist James Hetfield
responded to an advertisement posted by drummer Lars Ulrich in a local newspaper.

Metallica's current line-up comprises founding members Hetfield and Ulrich,
longtime lead guitarist Kirk Hammett and bassist Robert Trujillo.
